telepathy-salut|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
telepathy-salut: telepathy-salut (Link-local XMPP telepathy connection manager)
telepathy-salut:
telepathy-salut: telepathy-salut is a Telepathy connection manager for link-local XMPP.
telepathy-salut: Normally, XMPP does not support direct client-to-client interactions,
telepathy-salut: since it requires authentication with a server. This package makes
telepathy-salut: it is possible to establish an XMPP-like communications system on a
telepathy-salut: local network using zero-configuration networking.
telepathy-salut:
telepathy-salut: http://telepathy.freedesktop.org/wiki/FrontPage
